      "content": "You should focus on covering the \"pillars\" of appearance, communication, and cultural awareness. For appearance, emphasize tailored, conservative dressing that suggests high standards, regardless of the local norms. Communication should be about impeccable grammar and confident, yet deferential, interaction. Finally, cultural awareness is key, which means understanding the subtle ways different cultures value hierarchy and presentation.",
